Package com.oap2024team7.team7mediastreamingapp.utils

Class SessionData

java.lang.Object
com.oap2024team7.team7mediastreamingapp.utils.SessionData
public class SessionData extends Object
Class for the SessionData object. This class is responsible for managing the session data of the application. It stores the logged in customer, current profile, customer's address and selected film.
Author:
Agata (Agy) Olaussen (@agyCoding)
